e:T77d,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Salesforce Flow better than Zoho Flow?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Salesforce Flow scores 7.0 overall while Zoho Flow scores 6.0. Salesforce Flow is best for Salesforce admins and enterprises, while Zoho Flow excels for Zoho users and small businesses."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Salesforce Flow or Zoho Flow?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Salesforce Flow starts at Included and Zoho Flow starts at Free.  Zoho Flow offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Salesforce Flow to Zoho Flow?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Salesforce Flow and Zoho Flow support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Salesforce Flow vs Zoho Flow?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Salesforce Flow holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 4/10. Zoho Flow has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Salesforce Flow for extremely powerful for salesforce automation and Zoho Flow for excellent value within zoho ecosystem."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Salesforce Flow or Zoho Flow?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Salesforce Flow for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Zoho Flow remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize excellent value within zoho ecosystem. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML